      <title>价值 2050 亿美元的加密货币稳定币市场即将成为主流</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-31/crypto-s-205-billion-stablecoin-market-set-to-go-mainstream</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管比特币在 2024 年飙升至 100,000 美元以上成为头条新闻，但许多金融公司今年更加关注另一种类型的加密货币，其价格永远不会上涨或下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-31/crypto-s-205-billion-stablecoin-market-set-to-go-mainstream</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 31 Dec 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德的比特币基金成为“ETF 历史上最伟大的发行”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/blackrock-s-bitcoin-fund-became-greatest-launch-in-etf-history</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德公司 (BlackRock Inc.) 旗下的 iShares 部门在全球提供超过 1,400 只交易所交易基金，但没有一只基金的表现如此出色。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/blackrock-s-bitcoin-fund-became-greatest-launch-in-etf-history</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 14:12:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着购买量减少，MicroStrategy 购买了价值 2.09 亿美元的比特币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/microstrategy-buys-209-million-of-bitcoin-as-purchases-lessen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[MicroStrategy Inc. 表示，它购买了价值 2.09 亿美元的比特币，这是这家互联网时代软件制造商连续第八周购买原始加密货币的杠杆代理。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/microstrategy-buys-209-million-of-bitcoin-as-purchases-lessen</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 13:24:37 GMT</pubDate>
